title: 22 - Rosebud Baker
itunes:title: 22 - Rosebud Baker
description: Hot damn, it’s Rosebud Baker! If you don’t already know her from Comedy Central, Amazon’s Inside Jokes, or her hit podcast “Two Less Lonely Girls,” get ready to hear her now. We’re talking about everything from being disillusioned with your hometown to “exorcising the demons” from the special places is a past relationship to first date surprises gone awry. Here’s five words to describe this episode: don’t get on his motorcycle.
